Sentencas: Strontium substituted lanthanum manganite and yttria stabilized zirconia solid oxide fuel cell composite electrodes were impregnated with nano-particles of strontium substituted lanthanum manganite or alumina A clear positive effect was observed on low performing electrodes and on good performing electrodes if the temperature was kept low after the impregnation with strontium substituted lanthanum manganite.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of La0.85Sr0.15MnO3/yttria stabilized zirconia solid oxide fuel cell cathodes with La0.85Sr0.15MnO3 or Al2O3 nano-particles

Sentencas: On good performing electrodes the effect disappeared on heating.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of La0.85Sr0.15MnO3/yttria stabilized zirconia solid oxide fuel cell cathodes with La0.85Sr0.15MnO3 or Al2O3 nano-particles

Sentencas: Alumina nano-particles had a detrimental effect on the activity of the strontium substituted lanthanum manganite based electrodes.
Titulo: Effect of impregnation of La0.85Sr0.15MnO3/yttria stabilized zirconia solid oxide fuel cell cathodes with La0.85Sr0.15MnO3 or Al2O3 nano-particles
